reviews.title: “Mhz”
reviews.text: Overall the ram is good and fine working although it's a good ram it's not that high end ram...the discription says it's a 1600mhz ram..I got only 1333 MHz Ram..i was sad but the PC was fast,it could even run a game which I couldn't run before...to play heavy game we need a graphics card n this ram maybe it will work!am planning to buy a GPU....so but this ram at ur own risks because they can't exactly give u the same MHZ of the ram.it showed it is 1600mhz but I only got 1333mhz...thank you!
